      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Here you can find projects which exemplify different new features within the XPU and RIS toolset.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642725/solaris-studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=296\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642725/solaris-studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"563\" data-width=\"1200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642750\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"solaris-studio.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642725\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"7ecdbd04-b18c-48e9-bc5c-0e1c7193a0c1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642725/solaris-studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=563 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642725/solaris-studio.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105786&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=296 1x\"></span><p>Created by Pixar artist <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.artstation.com/eugeneriecansky\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eugene Riecansky</a>.</p><p>For more information about this great project, check out our <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-26.pixar.com/space/RFH26/19268259/Solaris+Studio\" rel=\"nofollow\">detailed docs</a>.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h3 id=\"ExamplesinSolaris-RenderManDigitalStudio\">RenderMan Digital Studio</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/renderman-examples/R27/RfS/SolarisDemoScene.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a></p><ul><li><p>Aces</p></li><li><p>Pixar Surface</p></li><li><p>USD Asset</p></li><li><p>Solaris </p></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642725/onward-Teapot-Lama-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=296\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642725/onward-Teapot-Lama-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433105785&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"563\" data-width=\"1200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642747\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"onward-Teapot-Lama-docs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-re